<p>Customise the header and the footer of your design. Display your own logo and design the footer content according to your requirements. The store features, for example, are a great way to highlight the features of your plentyShop, such as free shipping. You can link content categories in the <strong>Footer</strong> tab to display aditional information in the footer of plentyShop.</p>
