<p>Customise the design of the item view in the <strong>Item view</strong> tab. Select the item name and item information to be displayed in plentyShop. Furthermore, select which item variations should be displayed in the category view. For further information about saving the displayed texts in plentymarkets, refer to the <a href="/en/item/managing-items">managing items</a> page.</p>
